description = "This sector is NOT to be taken lightly. Multiple enemy bases have been located on this sector, some of them ferox, some of not, and they have come to a temporary truce, in order to deafeat you. Also, this sector contains silver you'll need to produce, reaserch, and use to your advantage.

Consider this a challenge sector. 
Good Luck, you'll need it."
